claim: Flublok is produced using a novel production platform in which recombinant HA is expressed in insect cells using a baculovirus expression vector system (BEVS).
explanation: A multi-row, multi-column table showing percentages of subjects reporting solicited adverse events (any, moderate, severe) after vaccination across various studies, with footnotes describing study details and reporting conventions.
